bitcoin
------------------------------------------
Bitcoin is an experimental digital currency that enables instant payments to
anyone, anywhere in the world. Bitcoin uses peer-to-peer technology to operate
with no central authority: managing transactions and issuing money are carried
out collectively by the network. Bitcoin Core is the name of open source
software which enables the use of this currency.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.1.2-1
  libbitcoinconsensus-devel-0.19.0.1-1bl1
  libbitcoinconsensus0-0.19.0.1-1bl1
  libboost_chrono1.66-1.66.0-1
  libboost_filesystem1.66-1.66.0-1
  libboost_system1.66-1.66.0-1
  libboost_test1.66-1.66.0-1
  libboost_thread1.66-1.66.0-1
  libevent2.0_5-2.0.22-1
  libgcc1-7.4.0-1
  libminiupnpc17-2.1-1bl1
  libprotobuf18-3.7.1-1
  libQt5Core5-5.9.4-2
  libQt5Gui5-5.9.4-2
  libsecp256k1_0-0.1+git20191230-1bl1
  libssl-devel-1.1.1d-1
  libssl1.1-1.1.1d-1
