Canonical website:
  https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/archive/v0.19.0.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack bitcoin-0.19.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./bitcoin-0.19.0.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/bitcoin-0.19.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/bitcoin-0.19.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbitcoinconsensus0-0.19.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbitcoinconsensus-devel-0.19.0.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

